All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClassificationDef, EntityDef, RelationshipDef
public abstract class TypeDef extends TypeDefSummary
The TypeDef is the base class for objects that store the properties of an open metadata type definition (call ed a TypeDef).

The different categories of Typedefs are listed in TypeDefCategory.
